	"\033[1;93m██████╔╝███████║██║██║     ██║   ██║███████╗██║   ██║██████╔╝███████║█████╗  ██████╔╝███████╗\033[m\n"\
	"\033[1;95m██╔═══╝ ██╔══██║██║██║     ██║   ██║╚════██║██║   ██║██╔═══╝ ██╔══██║██╔══╝  ██╔══██╗╚════██║\n"\
